Private Equity/Transaction Advisory: was an early member of the practice; promoted three times (manager, Director, Senior Director), helped establish the operational/technology, interim CIO services for private equity and merger integration playbook; performed diligence and First 100 Day planning for multi-billion-dollar acquisitions and held interim C-Level roles for several merger integration efforts.

